Troubleshooting Tips
Issue: Hydra connection timeout

Solution: Verify SSH service is running: sudo systemctl status ssh
Reduce thread count: Use -t 2 instead of -t 4
Issue: Permission denied errors

Solution: Ensure test users exist: cat /etc/passwd | grep testuser
Reset passwords: echo 'testuser1:password123' | sudo chpasswd
Issue: Python script import errors

Solution: Install required libraries: pip3 install paramiko
Verify Python version: python3 --version (should be 3.6+)
Issue: FTP connection refused

Solution: Check vsftpd status: sudo systemctl status vsftpd
Review configuration: sudo cat /etc/vsftpd.conf
Issue: No results found

Solution: Verify credentials exist in wordlists
Test manually first: ssh testuser1@127.0.0.1
